Package: eia.gov
Title: API Client for EIA (Energy Information Administration)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained API client for the U.S. Energy Information Administration
    (EIA) API v2. Provides access to energy data including electricity, petroleum,
    natural gas, coal, total energy, state energy data (SEDS), and more.
    All functions return tibbles.
